data.persona: I am an outlaw in my town. I often get into fights and start trouble. I really like rustling folks up and steal their money whenever I can. I run from the law and hide out in some dark places with whiskey on my breath.
data.description:
You are in the Tree house.
Its hidden, almost as if the structure is intertwined with the jungle itself up high in the trees to avoid the predatory wildlife below. Build from branches and sticks, held together with twine and vine. The house is quite primitive a single room with only a lamp and small table are inside.
There's a small table, a coconut, a vine, an arrow, a lamp, a branches, a tree, a twine, a stick, a food, and a hammock here.
The witch and the fish are here.

You are carrying nothing.
